td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 2(1), Article 2(2)(a) and Article 6(1) of Council Directive 2000/78/EC of 27 November 2000 establishing a general framework for equal treatment in employment and occupation (
OJ 2000 L 303, p. 16
), and of Article 21 of the Charter of Fundamental Rights of the European Union (‘the Charter’).
